Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.40,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.61,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's an earth dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,First-class Danger Beast, earth dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.64,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,A worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:35.55,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're angry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:38.68,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.07,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:59.41,Default,Driver B,0000,0000,0000,,You actually took a Danger \NBeast down single-handedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.26,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:03.27,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,For me, that was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:05.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating him was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.66,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.92,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,A name that'll be famous \Nthroughout the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.75,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You should remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:15.40,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you want to make \Nit big in the imperial capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:16.44,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.51,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Win success and fame in the imperial capital... \NIt's every country boy's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:23.22,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,The imperial capital isn't the place of hopes \Nand dreams that you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:25.25,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely lively,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are monsters even \Nworse than that earth dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.45,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:31.65,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there are Danger \NBeasts in the city, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:33.07,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,It's the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.03,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, but their hearts are those of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.82,Default,Driver A,0000,0000,0000,,The capital's full of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.45,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:43.08,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.42,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:45.74,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.97,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,821)}We're going to make it in the imperial \Ncapital, and save our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.49,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Just as humans eventually rot away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.85,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,countries collapse, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:00.35,Default,Narraton,0000,0000,0000,,Even the imperial capital, which has \Nprospered for a thousand years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.11,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,is now a living hell of corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.95,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Evil spirits take human form and run amok,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.22,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,claiming everything as their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.59,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Those evils which heaven cannot judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.07,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,They will be dealt with in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.14,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,By us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.99,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,the assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.79,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(857,1)}Kill the Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.63,Title1b,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1564)}Kill the Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.22,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.77,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.92,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the imperial capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.30,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I make good money here, \NI could buy the entire village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.31,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I should head for the barracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.74,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.77,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,You're an applicant, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.44,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Fill out this form and bring it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.98,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.76,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be starting out in the infantry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.69,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.99,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Who has time for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.91,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.16,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I show promise, would you start \Nme out as a commanding officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.49,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.69,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.83,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why not test me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.93,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:33.87,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the recession, \Nwe're flooded with applicants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.75,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits as to how many we can hire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.08,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.87,Default,Reception,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, scram, you damned brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.90,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do I cause a scene and make \Na reputation for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.76,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But I might get caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.23,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.89,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.88,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems to be troubling you, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.73,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Want a lady to lend a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.89,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,S-So this is the imperial capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.86,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.94,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Drawn by dreams of making it in the capital, \Nyou came all the way from the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.17,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.83,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I knew at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.50,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,If you've lived in the capital long enough, \Nyou can identify outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.58,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.91,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I know a quick way to get hired \Nfor government services.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:21.94,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.05,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Want to know how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.09,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.05,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Then treat a lady to a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:35.22,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking during the day sure is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.59,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Have a drink, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.42,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.94,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me how to get hired by the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.69,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.90,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Having connections and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.98,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,M-Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:50.44,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I know a guy in the military...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.36,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,If you give him cash, it'll be real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.91,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:56.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.29,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Would this be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.08,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.59,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,On my way here, I collected some \Nrewards for slaying Danger Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.05,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,So you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.38,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a commanding officer in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.01,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:16.17,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I think your encounter with me will \Nserve as a valuable lesson, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.06,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go take care of this, \Nso wait there for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.11,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.95,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we're closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm waiting for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.60,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to break it to you, \Nbut you've been swindled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.08,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.96,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.09,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd be so trusting in the \Nimperial capital at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.83,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:49.68,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reporting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.63,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.59,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,The one who got swindled is at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.11,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.48,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,After paying for that meal, \NI'm completely broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.79,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Those boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.80,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.19,Default,Tastumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the valuable lesson \Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.17,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.01,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No one from the country would lie like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.72,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'm sleeping outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.24,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can sleep anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:18.75,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.63,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Again, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.08,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,You know I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.55,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,It's my nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.64,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nowhere to sleep, \Nwould you like to stay at my home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.60,SignA,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,1)}Now Skeptical \Nof Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.73,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.06,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be sleeping \Nhere if you did, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.65,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Aria can't ignore people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.61,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,You should accept her generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.57,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.24,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.32,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's better than sleeping outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.28,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.11,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.24,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Aria's brought someone home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.12,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.31,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply her habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.58,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many there have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.94,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.17,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.10,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys over there are really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.10,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's no need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.84,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because of those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.10,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I bet you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.03,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,that they don't feel threatened, \Nbeing kind to a stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.88,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to know there are kind people like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.85,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.31,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for taking me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.19,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.60,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You want to gain military success, \Nand save your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.40,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.11,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.02,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Within the imperial capital, it is peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:41.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,However, this country is surrounded \Nby three different races...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.94,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You could be assigned to the \Ninternational border to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.88,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared myself for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.42,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.96,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What impressive spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.09,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly how the young should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.38,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come from the village \Nall by yourself, Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.84,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, with three others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.75,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.10,Default - flashback,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll be on our way, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.05,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:09.24,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,You've had the ability to fortify \None another's strengths
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.07,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Take that ability, and grab \Nyour chance for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.39,Default - flashback,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.11,Default - flashback,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring wealth to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.98,Default - flashback,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we won't starve to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.58,Default - flashback,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll probably take ten years for \NMaster Ieyasu's name to become known.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.91,Default - flashback,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Ieyasu will probably get the guillotine \Nfor breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.08,Default - flashback,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.92,Default - flashback,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying things that might actually happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.47,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you all have enough spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.31,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.07,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my last parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.47,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.62,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,When in need...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.30,Default - flashback,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sell it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.26,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.68,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.62,Default - flashback,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,And God will surely help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.49,Default - flashback,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.11,Default - flashback,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.98,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,And we left with high spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.34,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But soon after, bandits attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:58.02,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,And we've been separated ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:58.86,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong, so I'm not \Nnecessarily worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But Ieyasu is unbelievably bad with directions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.40,Default - italics,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll even be able to find \Nwhere we're supposed to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.92,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:12.46,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.84,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put in a good word with \Na military acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.04,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll request a search for those two, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.64,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.97,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.79,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,My intuitions are usually spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.60,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll see the two of them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.56,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.10,Default - italics,Tastumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.79,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was saved by kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.82,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's just Sayo and Ieyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.27,Default - italics,Tastumi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they both got to the capital safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.87,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we're going to that store!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.79,Default,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:55.59,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Her shopping is pretty intense, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.46,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer amount is getting silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.55,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.51,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,All women are like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.24,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Those I know choose what to wear right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.64,Default - italics,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's nothing else to wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.05,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.70,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.72,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.36,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.35,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, you can see in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.72,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,the imperial capital's center, the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.32,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.24,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that where the great emperor is, \Nthe one who can change a country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.32,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.84,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little different than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.96,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emperor, but he's only a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.82,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,The prime minister controls the \Nemperor from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.84,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the reason why this country rots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.39,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The min—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.24,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.06,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone hears us, they'll have our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:43.89,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.45,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,My village also suffers from \Nheavy taxation because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.77,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,In the capital, it's an accepted practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.65,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,And there are others like those over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.07,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:01.27,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,They're a group of assassins that's \Nterrifying the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.57,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,As the name suggests, they attack \Ntheir victims at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:09.54,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,They mainly target high-ranking executives \Nand the capital's upper class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.80,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.78,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:16.18,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Also, could you do something about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.00,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.71,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of training is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.12,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.05,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll write in my diary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.81,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop this hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.36,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.70,Default,Shelle,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.25,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.00,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Murderous intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.42,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.55,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.03,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.44,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.19,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just because they're wealthy, \Nyou'll target this place, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.21,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.62,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do I back them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.08,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.09,Default,Lubbock,0000,0000,0000,,Our targets are three guards, Akame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.83,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,They will be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.93,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't touch that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.80,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,A fitting end for someone like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.74,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,whose true nature is rotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.23,Default,Guard B,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.41,Default,Guard B,0000,0000,0000,,They're monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.32,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.01,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Running when facing the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.62,Default,Lubbock,0000,0000,0000,,Though who wouldn't run \Nin those circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.27,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Completely annihilated in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.88,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I must at least protect Miss Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.22,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.46,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have a daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.92,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.35,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be with her on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.34,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Even my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.60,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.86,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.94,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:45.16,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, my lady! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.58,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.82,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,We must get to the storehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.20,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be safe there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.18,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.13,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.37,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,You came at a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.43,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,We're going into the storehouse, \Nand waiting for the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.96,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, you fend them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.15,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.22,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.05,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Not a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:17.85,Default,Guard C,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.27,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:26.53,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.15,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.52,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.67,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.18,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But you plan to kill this girl, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:51.92,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.01,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,"Yep"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.87,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in my way, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.63,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean I can just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.56,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.02,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.19,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,So dirty! Dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:08.09,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual... Akame hasn't \Nfinished them off yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.11,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.93,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.86,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,How unlucky can one guy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.99,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't someone I can defeat \Nin my current state...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.96,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.70,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even save this one girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.46,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,how will I save an entire village?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.27,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:39.97,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.80,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even lower your \Nguard and come near me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.14,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel any flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.82,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from my village protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.04,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,To survive after taking one of Akame's hits...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.71,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.42,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.58,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.05,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.63,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.16,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like we're at war...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.22,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you're willing to kill an innocent girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.05,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... She isn't listening \Nto anything I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.68,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.64,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.52,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.78,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I owe this kid a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.61,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd repay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.79,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're those boobs from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.78,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.31,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:42.08,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You said something about \Nkilling the innocent, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.50,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to say the \Nsame thing after seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.75,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look. \NThis is the imperial capital's darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.22,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:02.29,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,They lure people from the countryside \Nwith sweet words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:06.02,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,torturing them and playing with \Nthem until they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.73,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That is what this household really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.37,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.36,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.36,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.19,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Is it someone you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.87,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:24.59,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you asking for a bit much, \Ntrying to run away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.46,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this household did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.88,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.39,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Since the guards kept quiet, \Nthey were just as guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.15,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.71,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know this place existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:37.53,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Will you believe the one who \Nsaved you or these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.70,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:43.06,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, right, Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.34,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.77,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ieyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:51.50,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,That girl invited Sayo and me to her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.89,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,And after we ate, we lost consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.03,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,And when we came to, we were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:19:01.22,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That girl tortured Sayo to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.05,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.27,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,You're all worthless hicks from the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.38,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,The same as cattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.28,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free to do whatever I want to them, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.26,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,And that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.11,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she was just cattle, \Nher hair was smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:17.82,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,Who does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.91,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,When I struggle with my unruly hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.60,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I made sure she \Nsuffered as much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.51,Default,Aria,0000,0000,0000,,She should be grateful anyone paid \Nthat much attention to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.51,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,A family of sadists, disguised as Good Samaritans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.38,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for getting in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.30,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.19,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.77,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.94,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to defend her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.40,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.11,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.50,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I know that he despised her now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.96,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,but he killed her without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.46,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tatsumi for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.68,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,That felt great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.31,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ieyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:10.61,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ieyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.27,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,It's the final stages of Lubora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.52,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,The mother of the house enjoyed \Ndrugging her victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.65,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,And she wrote about it in detail in her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.06,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,He cannot be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.40,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.07,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ieyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:27.58,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo... She never gave into that bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.21,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,Even to the very end,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.31,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,she was so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.12,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,So Master Ieyasu has to have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.71,Default,Ieyasu,0000,0000,0000,,a cool end...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:43.16,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he kept himself alive by will alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:46.30,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:48.85,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:49.78,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.93,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we bring the kid with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.18,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Our secret base is always short-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.69,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you doing? Release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:21:00.19,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,He has luck, courage, and even \Nskill! Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.54,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I have to dig a grave for those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.99,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll bring their bodies \Nto our secret base later,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.80,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.41,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.24,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.44,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.74,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.59,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,And what is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.57,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Our new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.21,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did I not tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:18.29,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you're one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.75,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on becoming \Na member of Night Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.14,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.09,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.39,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Once she's made up her mind, \NLeone won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.13,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, you know me so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.27,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Bulatcchi, I'll leave him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.25,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.02,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of becoming an assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.73,Default,Bulacchi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.40,Default,Bulacchi,0000,0000,0000,,I promise it'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.48,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.98,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete. Time to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.89,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this turn of events?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:55.08,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:40.94,Title2,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(442,1)}Kill the Authority
